## English Version

### 1. Grant of Rights (Free of Charge)

The copyright holder grants you a royalty-free right to use, copy, modify,
create derivative works of, and redistribute this software, subject to the
conditions below.

- **Any use including commercial operations**: including use by individuals
  or companies in construction or consulting business activities.
- **Use via AI tools**: including operating, analyzing, or modifying this
  software through AI agents or AI tools that assist human use.
- **Embedding and redistribution (OEM)**: embedding into your own products
  or services and redistribution are permitted subject to the attribution
  requirement in Section 3.

### 2. Limitations

The following require a separate commercial license agreement with
Tatelog Inc.:

a. **Providing a managed service**: providing this software or derivative
   works to third parties as a hosted or managed service.

b. **Use as an integration API or automated processing platform**:
   providing or using this software or derivative works for programmatic
   integration with external systems (offering APIs, automated
   system-to-system data exchange, headless execution platforms, etc.).
   Use via AI tools assisting human operation (Section 1) is not subject
   to this limitation.

c. **Removing license or credit notices**: removing or altering copyright
   notices, license notices, or attribution included in this software.

### 3. Attribution

When redistributing this software or derivative works, or embedding them
into your own products, display the following credit in a location visible
to users (in-app display, documentation, etc.):

